                                "text": " \"You're right that modal dialogs aren't exactly the same thing as Vim's modes. I'd actually not connected the two until Bret Victor mentioned Vim above. It might have been some creative license, since Larry Tesler's work seems to mostly predate Bill Joy's creation of vi.\""
